column1: # The station number (originally 2546/5) changed in 1938, resulting in a second 1930s sheet being used.
# The December 1938 figure is identified as a part-estimate due to snow on the sheet and has been retained.
# The February 1947 figure is identified as a part-estimate due to snow on the sheet and has been retained.
# The station continued until 2002 according to MIDAS.
